{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went to Guben.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A woman, yeah, girls-- all girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, I want to say I remember that about a man's barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right there, there was a man's barrack, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw-- I saw corpses there, outside-- you know, because in the evening, [? the whole thing. ?] And there, I saw one, as I said.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't see him running to the-- to the electricity, but he was just hanging there on the thing, and things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to Guben, and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- I think it was more pleasant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more pleasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- again, with the bucket in the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came there in the evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that, because it's further than from the-- from Auschwitz to Plaszow, because that's like in the middle of Germany, almost.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't look how far it is, which way from Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did found it on the-- on the thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the map.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there we found out that there is a munitions factory in-- in the city, not in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came-- it was in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought, compared to other places, it looked like a sanatorium, because there was not too many women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we all-- they all had that grey dresses, and everybody had a towel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from the towel, they made a turban.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the woman looked so nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we were without hair, and the turban on the head, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was so quiet in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people which were there, already, they were kind of running around, and accepting us, and everything is shh, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And assigned to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
